Face Painting

desc: Want to paint your friend’s face? It’s fun! 
Face painting is artistically applying paint to a person’s face. Drag your friend along.
 A theme will be given on spot.
participation: 2 per team

rules: 
1. It is an event for 2 participants.
2. Participants must bring their own materials.
3. Duration of the event will be 90 minutes.
CAUTION: MAKE SURE YOUR PAINTS ARE SKIN FRIENDLY

eventco: Chandini Sharma - 8123919619 
prize: 1st place:₹2000    2nd place:₹1000
     
registration: ₹200
